ham/Northumberland 1]] there would be no relegation this season. |group=a}} || Durham/Northumberland Division 2\n|-\n| 2009-10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.englandrugby.com/fixtures-and-results/competitions/northern-division/2009-2010/group/13584|title=2009-10 Northern Division|publisher=England Rugby|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref> || 12 || style=\"background:#d8ffeb;\"| '''[[Ponteland RFC|Ponteland]]''' || style=\"background:#d8ffeb;\"| [[Medicals RFC|Medicals]] || [[Houghton Rugby Club|Houghton]], [[North Shields RFC|North Shields]] || Durham/Northumberland Division 2\n|-\n| 2010-11<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.englandrugby.com/fixtures-and-results/competitions/northern-division/2010-2011/group/14456|title=2010-11 Northern Division|publisher=England Rugby|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref> || 12 || style=\"background:#d8ffeb;\"| '''[[Guisborough RUFC|Guisborough]]''' || style=\"background:#d8ffeb;\"| [[Acklam RUFC|Acklam]] || [[Prudhoe and Stocksfield RUFC|Prudhoe & Stocksfield]] || Durham/Northumberland Division 2\n|-\n| 2011-12<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.englandrugby.com/fixtures-and-results/competitions/northern-division/2011-2012/group/15365|title=2011-12 Northern Division|publisher=England Rugby|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref> || 13 || style=\"background:#d8ffeb;\"| '''[[Blyth RFC|Blyth]]''' || style=\"background:#d8ffeb;\"| [[Consett RFC|Consett]] || [[Yarm Rugby Club|Yarm]], [[Whitby RUFC|Whitby]] || Durham/Northumberland Division 2\n|-\n| 2012-13<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.englandrugby.com/fixtures-and-results/competitions/northern-division/2012-2013/group/16303|title=2012-13 Northern Division|publisher=England Rugby|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref> || 13 || style=\"background:#d8ffeb;\"| '''[[Bishop Auckland RUFC|Bishop Auckland]]''' || style=\"background:#d8ffeb;\"| [[Novocastrians Rugby Football Club|Novocastrians]] || [[Winlaton Vulcans RFC|Winlaton Vulcans]], [[Seaham RUFC|Seaham]] || Durham/Northumberland Division 2\n|-\n| 2013-14<ref>{{cite